2/7/00
    BUG: After forced switch from AD1 to AD2, the refPicNo is not correctly
         set, which causes AD2 to switch back to live very soon.  Setting of
         refPicNo to the picNo of the first picture in the queue failed,
         possibily such a picture is missing.
